</problem>
<solution id="fs-id1167835503875">
<para id="fs-id1167832116054"><newline/><media id="fs-id1167835503877" alt="The figure shows a graph of a straight line on the x y-coordinate plane. The x and y-axes run from negative 12 to 12. The straight line goes through the points (negative 9, negative 1), (negative 6, 0), (negative 3, 1), (0, 2), (3, 3), (6, 4), and (9, 5).">
