<para id="fs-id1167834377227"><newline/><media id="fs-id1167832151040" alt="The figure shows a graph of a straight line on the x y-coordinate plane. The x and y-axes run from negative 12 to 12. The straight line goes through the points (negative 1, negative 4), (0, 0), and (1, 4).">
