</problem>
<solution id="fs-id1167831911373">
<para id="fs-id1167830964089"><span class="token">ⓐ</span> A: yes, B: no, C: yes, D: yes <span class="token">ⓑ</span> A: yes, B: no, C: yes, D: yes</para>
